title: CNN panel reacts to Bill Maher's bleak 2024 election prediction
description: CNN panelists Alice Stewart and April Ryan discuss comedian Bill Maher's provocative election prediction.

title: Madonna flashes audience on 'The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon'
description: The pop icon was on Fallon's show promoting her new documentary "Madame X" when she decided to make some "good trouble."

title: River of volcanic lava engulfs home
description: Buildings near the volcano on the Spanish island of La Palma were engulfed by rivers of lava. Reuters captured video of one home surrounded by lava.
